Text:
When you email an O2 venue requesting a wheelchair space and carer ticket and you get back “you have booked balcony early entry”

Bab, that’s…not what i asked for?!

@O2ForumKTown can we give me the accessibility I’ve actually requested please?

Me: trying to get European breakdown cover for the chair since @MotabilityOps insure the chair abroad but won’t do breakdown cover

@MotabilityOps : Check with your dealership, they should be able to give recommendations

Dealership: We have no idea why they asked you to call us

When the band are saying doors at 6, but venue website and social media and my companion ticket all say doors at 7 😂

Which is it?! 😂

@O2InstituteBham what time are doors for @TheSherlocks tonight? because there appears to be confusion somewhere

