My #LastFourWatched for #LetterboxdFriday.

It's been a busy week (with two Mai Zetterling double bills last weekend), so some of my faves have dropped off this graphic.

DESPERATE MOMENT (1953, 4 stars);
BLACKMAILED (1951, 3.5);
THE ROMANTIC AGE (1949, 3.5)
JET STORM (1959, 3.5) https://t.co/LHtIrG1UtL

